-- Morales Says He Won't Hesitate to Expel USAID From Bolivia, La Razon Says
-- Sara Shahriari
-- 2010-06-23T15:14:35Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-23/morales-says-he-won-t-hesitate-to-expel-usaid-from-bolivia-la-razon-says.html

          
          
             Bolivian President  Evo Morales  said
yesterday he would not hesitate to expel USAID from the country,
 La Razon reported .  
 Morales has accused the organization of infiltrating social
movements through non-governmental organizations in an attempt
to destabilize the government, the La Paz-based daily newspaper
said.  
 Leaders of several indigenous groups demanded the
government present proof of USAID’s interference in social
movements, and asked for the organization’s expulsion if
interference is proven, La Razon reported.  
